<p>
<b><font color=#113377 size=+2 >Attributes</font></b>



<dl>

<p><dt><tt><b><a name="background_image">background_image</a></b></tt>=<i>path</i>
<dd>
Set the background image to use.




<p><dt><tt><b><a name="delay">delay</a></b></tt>

<dd>
Set the delay between the frames in the animation.



<p><dt><tt><b><a name="time_offset">time_offset</a></b></tt>

<dd>
Add or subtract a number of seconds to the actual time.



</dl>










